科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 预告 Slipknot 的“失落”专辑《Look Outside Your Window》即将发行https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-teases-release-of-slipknots-lost-album-look-outside-your-window-3482056?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=corey-taylor-戏弄释放滑结丢失专辑看看窗外Damian JonesSun, 13 Aug 2023 13:37:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3482056 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="科里·泰勒" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队几年前录制了这张唱片</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-teases-release-of-slipknots-lost-album-look-outside-your-window-3482056">科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 预告 Slipknot 的“失落”专辑《Look Outside Your Window》的发布</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="科里·泰勒" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_coreytaylor_danvirchow_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor)</a>预告了活结<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">(Slipknot</a> ) 丢失的专辑《Look Outside Your Window》的发行。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/corey-taylor-interview-cmf2-ptsd-slipknot-look-outside-your-window-3480518">科里·泰勒：“不要觉得自己很特别——我讨厌所有人！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该歌曲由主唱 Sid Wilson、Jim Root 和 Shawn &#39;Clown&#39; Crahan 录制，当时乐队正在制作 2008 年的专辑《All Hope Is Gone》。有一次，泰勒试图将两张唱片合二为一，但“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-slipknot-all-hope-is-hope-gone-outtakes-experimental-radiohead-2541951">超级实验性的、充满活力的</a>”曲目并没有融合在一起。迄今为止，仅发布了一首曲目——“All Hope Is Gone”的附赠曲目“Til We Die”。</p><p>此后，乐队多次谈到发行这张丢失的专辑。 Clown <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/slipknot-clown-new-guy-tortilla-man-knotfest-we-are-not-your-kind-knotfest-cruise-look-outside-your-window-2601547">在 2020 年接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>透露，乐队几乎在 2019 年圣诞节期间放弃了它，但最终决定不这样做，因为他们不希望它干扰第六张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/slipknot-we-are-not-your-kind-review-2534063">We Are Not Your Kind</a> 》。</p><p>一月份，克拉汉表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lost-slipknot-album-look-outside-your-window-could-be-released-this-year-says-clown-3373724">，今年终于可以见到曙光，但迄今为止尚未实现</a>。</p><p>现在，在接受<em>NME 的新采访时，</em>泰勒<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lost-slipknot-album-look-outside-your-window-could-be-released-this-year-says-clown-3373724">给出了进一步的更新，并表示专辑尚未发行部分是他的错</a>。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/slipknot-clown@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">活结乐队的肖恩·“小丑”·克拉汉。图片来源：弗朗西斯科·普兰多尼/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>当被问及这张唱片时，他回答说：“你提到这个实际上很有趣。有一天我和小丑谈论这件事，他说，“它没有问世的原因之一是因为你一直在发布垃圾，这与我想发布它的时间一直相冲突！”我当时想，‘操老兄，你为什么不告诉我？’他说，“操，泰勒——你真是太狗屎了！”听起来他终于可以锁定发布日期了，我已经向他保证我不会发布任何会破坏这一日期的内容。我想这将是明年——终于，伙计！</p><p>泰勒继续说道：“我刚刚回去听了所有这些东西，它们太棒了，太不同了。人们认为这听起来像“活结”，活结是非常错误的。这听起来不像活结乐队曾经做过的任何事情，这就是为什么它有自己的特色。对我来说，这确实是一张久违的专辑。音乐是如此美妙，它可能有一些我最喜欢的旋律，人们真的会喜欢它。小丑做得非常好。”</p><p>与此同时，泰勒最近谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-says-a-lot-of-people-in-iowa-are-very-ashamed-slipknot-are-from-there-3480670">活结乐队家乡爱荷华州的人们多年来对乐队的反应</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Corey Taylor 谈论“CMF2”、PTSD 意识以及 Slipknot 的下一步发展" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jhKn5spvKbQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他地方，泰勒此前宣布即将为他的第二张个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknots-corey-taylor-shares-update-as-he-starts-work-on-second-solo-album-3385527">“CMFT2”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-announces-cmft2-uk-and-european-tour-preorder-listen-new-single-3467850">进行英国和欧洲巡演</a>。</p><p>从 11 月 8 日开始，巡演将以在利兹 O2 学院的一场演出拉开帷幕，随后第二天在伍尔弗汉普顿举行演出。从那里开始，泰勒将在曼彻斯特、格拉斯哥和伦敦等城市停留。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcorey-taylor-tickets%2Fartist%2F1608825" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买门票。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-teases-release-of-slipknots-lost-album-look-outside-your-window-3482056">科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 预告 Slipknot 的“失落”专辑《Look Outside Your Window》的发布</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
对 WOMAD 音乐节疾病病例的调查尚无定论https://www.nme.com/news/music/investigation-into-sickness-cases-at-womad-festival-inconclusive-3482040?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=investigation-into-sickness-cases-at-womad-节日未定论Damian JonesSun, 13 Aug 2023 12:32:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3482040 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="WOMAD 音乐节" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>事件发生后报告了少量腹泻病例</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/investigation-into-sickness-cases-at-womad-festival-inconclusive-3482040">《对 WOMAD 音乐节上的疾病病例调查尚无定论》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="WOMAD 音乐节" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>对今年 WOMAD 音乐节后的一些疾病病例进行的调查尚未得出结论。</p><p>此前，7 月 27 日至 30 日在马姆斯伯里举行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/investigation-launched-into-sickness-cases-at-womad-festival-3479268">的活动结束后，报告了少量腹泻病例</a><em>。</em></p><p>英国健康安全局（UKHSA）发起了一项调查，但目前尚未得出结论。</p><p>阿拉斯代尔·伍德博士告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-wiltshire-66477991" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司新闻</em></a>，虽然该机构“考虑了不同的潜在原因”，包括食物、水、厕所和卫生设施，以及受影响人群的样本结果（如有），但进行的测试并未发现“单一原因” 。</p><p> “考虑到事件发生的时间已经过去，进一步的测试不太可能揭示任何其他信息，”他补充道。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_womad_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 7 月 28 日，英格兰马姆斯伯里查尔顿公园举行的 WOMAD 音乐节上的人群。图片来源：C Brandon/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p> UKHSA 表示，尚未发现节日期间报告的疾病存在任何持续的公共卫生风险，并且“报告患病的人数占节日观众总数的比例很小”。</p><p>调查结束后，WOMAD 组织者向<em>NME</em>发表声明称：“在 UKHSA 考虑了不同的潜在原因以及受影响人群样本的结果后，我们非常欣慰地得知，疫情的影响范围有限，而且没有证据表明支持任何关于 WOMAD 作为节日制作者或我们的任何合作伙伴（包括食品贸易商）在现场采取的行动可能导致疾病的担忧。</p><p> “这不会以任何方式减少我们对受影响者的关心，我们祝愿他们早日康复。我们要感谢与我们分享有关他们的症状以及今年在 WOMAD 节上经历的信息的公众。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/femi-kuti">Femi Kuti</a> 、 <a href="/artists/bombay-bicycle-club">Bombay Bicycle Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cinematic-orchestra">Cinematic Orchestra</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soul-ii-soul">Soul II Soul</a> 、Emicida、47Soul、Jungle Brothers、Ana Tijoux、Tank &amp; The Bangas 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enny">ENNY</a>均在今年的音乐节上表演。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/investigation-into-sickness-cases-at-womad-festival-inconclusive-3482040">《对 WOMAD 音乐节上的疾病病例调查尚无定论》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
